div.div: Late music icon Zex Manatsa's widow, Stella, dies - NewZimbabwe.com

Spread This NewsBy Staff Reporter THE widow of one of Zimbabwes most celebrated yester-year musicians, Zex Manatsa, Stella Manatsa, has died. Her untimely passing on comes eight months following the death of her husband. Tendai Manatsa, son to the iconic couple, confirmed the sad development through a post on social media this Tuesday.
